          %p Dying to know who's going to be on-hand? We'll announce our first musical guest after we raise $500 for Nairobi Dev School.
          %p <a class="button radius" href="http://www.indiegogo.com/projects/hypeharvest-nairobi-dev-school/">Or you can unlock a musical guest!</a>

